1
00:02:18,679 --> 00:02:20,759
I never expected the snowy scenery of Lone Mountain to be so beautiful.

2
00:02:21,759 --> 00:02:22,720
If Linlang saw this,

3
00:02:23,279 --> 00:02:24,479
she would definitely be very happy.

4
00:02:40,520 --> 00:02:41,399
Why is it you again?

5
00:02:42,440 --> 00:02:44,160
Do you really not want to see me that much?

6
00:02:44,440 --> 00:02:45,919
I've told you many times already.

7
00:02:47,080 --> 00:02:47,960
In the past,

8
00:02:48,160 --> 00:02:49,880
I did live as Fei Ying.

9
00:02:50,279 --> 00:02:51,360
But that was in the past.

10
00:02:52,839 --> 00:02:53,839
You've seen it yourself.

11
00:02:54,080 --> 00:02:54,800
Tomorrow,

12
00:02:55,240 --> 00:02:56,800
I will marry Linlang.

13
00:02:58,399 --> 00:03:00,399
So today, I want to try one last time.

14
00:03:01,000 --> 00:03:03,119
I don't believe Fei Ying has just disappeared.

15
00:03:05,759 --> 00:03:07,520
The Tianchi artifact, the Soul Severing Cord, erased your memories.

16
00:03:08,039 --> 00:03:10,240
Before you lost your memory, you went to the Tianchi cemetery.

17
00:03:10,479 --> 00:03:11,080
There,

18
00:03:11,160 --> 00:03:13,039
you found traces of the Wuxiang treasure.

19
00:03:13,479 --> 00:03:15,039
But you were also seriously injured by the artifact.

20
00:03:15,320 --> 00:03:16,880
That's why you lost your memory in Mist Town.

21
00:03:16,960 --> 00:03:17,600
Today

22
00:03:17,759 --> 00:03:19,880
is my last chance to bring you back.

23
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:28,160
Sentiment

24
00:03:28,479 --> 00:03:31,240
is the most useless thing in this world.

25
00:03:31,720 --> 00:03:32,960
These lashes

26
00:03:33,440 --> 00:03:36,160
are your punishment for disobeying my orders.

27
00:03:36,839 --> 00:03:37,639
Fei Ying,

28
00:03:38,600 --> 00:03:41,399
your entire purpose for existing is the Wuxiang treasure.

29
00:03:41,600 --> 00:03:43,399
You trained hard in Dugu City for over ten years.

30
00:03:43,479 --> 00:03:46,080
You became the top master of the inner court for this very day.

31
00:03:46,320 --> 00:03:48,039
If you can't find the Wuxiang treasure,

32
00:03:48,199 --> 00:03:49,720
then don't come back.

33
00:03:50,559 --> 00:03:51,520
You are my father.

34
00:03:51,679 --> 00:03:52,639
Why

35
00:03:52,839 --> 00:03:55,559
in the face of wealth that rivals a nation,

36
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:58,240
does so-called family mean nothing?

37
00:03:58,919 --> 00:04:01,360
This is the first lesson your father teaches you.

38
00:04:01,960 --> 00:04:04,360
It might also be the last.

39
00:04:06,279 --> 00:04:07,679
The Wuxiang treasure

40
00:04:07,839 --> 00:04:11,559
will ultimately be mine, Dugu Wumo's.

41
00:04:21,279 --> 00:04:22,160
Lu Jiu

42
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:38,920
Lu Jiu

43
00:04:51,440 --> 00:04:52,720
Senior Sister, are you alright?

44
00:04:55,279 --> 00:04:56,079
Fei Ying

45
00:04:57,320 --> 00:04:58,640
You finally came back.

46
00:05:00,079 --> 00:05:01,119
It's time for us

47
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:02,559
to go back.

48
00:05:03,440 --> 00:05:04,679
I've waited for this day

49
00:05:04,959 --> 00:05:06,200
for seven years.

50
00:05:07,480 --> 00:05:08,320
Lu Jiu

51
00:05:17,760 --> 00:05:18,839
Lu Jiu, Lu Jiu

52
00:05:19,279 --> 00:05:20,519
Have you forgotten?

53
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:21,839
You said

54
00:05:22,119 --> 00:05:24,519
you would stay with me for life and protect me.

55
00:05:25,040 --> 00:05:26,040
I'm not Lu Jiu.

56
00:05:27,239 --> 00:05:28,440
I'm Fei Ying.

57
00:05:48,440 --> 00:05:50,720
By the Mandate of Heaven, the Emperor decrees:

58
00:05:50,959 --> 00:05:52,839
Geng Zhao has neglected his duties.

59
00:05:52,880 --> 00:05:54,160
He has deceived the Emperor and defied authority.

60
00:05:54,200 --> 00:05:55,839
He is to be relieved of all positions effective immediately.

61
00:05:55,880 --> 00:05:57,600
He shall be imprisoned in the Tianluo prison.

62
00:05:57,640 --> 00:05:58,799
This is the imperial command.

63
00:06:03,440 --> 00:06:04,559
I have disobeyed the imperial edict.

64
00:06:04,679 --> 00:06:05,760
I accept my punishment.

65
00:06:06,359 --> 00:06:08,799
Even if Your Majesty does not believe Fengleitang is innocent,

66
00:06:09,119 --> 00:06:09,760
the case

67
00:06:09,839 --> 00:06:11,399
I should still be sent to the Ministry of Justice for trial.

68
00:06:11,679 --> 00:06:12,640
Why is it Tianluo prison?

69
00:06:12,799 --> 00:06:13,799
Lord Geng,

70
00:06:13,880 --> 00:06:15,600
you have served in the Investigation Bureau for many years.

71
00:06:15,799 --> 00:06:18,480
Do you still not understand His Majesty's intentions?

72
00:06:19,279 --> 00:06:21,040
Failing to eliminate Gushan is a minor issue.

73
00:06:21,359 --> 00:06:22,640
Harboring traitors

74
00:06:22,679 --> 00:06:24,799
is the true reason for your conviction.

75
00:06:25,760 --> 00:06:26,559
Take him away.

76
00:06:28,720 --> 00:06:29,519
Wait.

77
00:06:31,839 --> 00:06:32,640
I, Geng Zhao,

78
00:06:32,679 --> 00:06:34,040
have dared to return to the capital to report.

79
00:06:34,200 --> 00:06:35,359
I will not run away.

80
00:06:35,640 --> 00:06:36,480
Sir,

81
00:06:37,079 --> 00:06:37,839
Stand down.

82
00:07:04,640 --> 00:07:05,440
Linlang

83
00:07:05,760 --> 00:07:07,359
Your body can't handle it if you keep going like this.

84
00:07:07,559 --> 00:07:09,399
Even if I recover, what difference does it make?

85
00:07:09,600 --> 00:07:10,720
What do you mean by that?

86
00:07:11,640 --> 00:07:12,760
Is there really no one else in this world

87
00:07:13,079 --> 00:07:15,000
but Lu Jiu who is worth your concern?

88
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:17,799
The Linlang who once wanted to serve the people

89
00:07:17,839 --> 00:07:19,160
and solve cases to catch criminals,

90
00:07:19,519 --> 00:07:20,559
where has she gone?

91
00:07:22,160 --> 00:07:24,279
I understand how you feel right now.

92
00:07:24,399 --> 00:07:26,160
Back then, when Lu Jiu was still an infant,

93
00:07:26,239 --> 00:07:27,320
he was taken away.

94
00:07:27,959 --> 00:07:30,480
I also thought I would never see him again in this life.

95
00:07:30,799 --> 00:07:33,119
But I kept searching and waiting.

96
00:07:33,320 --> 00:07:34,760
Even though twenty years passed,

97
00:07:34,959 --> 00:07:36,640
didn't I still get him back in the end?

98
00:07:38,640 --> 00:07:40,200
You mean

99
00:07:40,799 --> 00:07:43,200
Fei Ying took seven years to recover his memory.

100
00:07:43,399 --> 00:07:45,880
I can also wait for Lu Jiu to regain his memory.

101
00:07:50,519 --> 00:07:51,959
I'll wait with you.

102
00:08:14,799 --> 00:08:15,399
Hyah!

103
00:08:15,640 --> 00:08:16,119
Hyah!

104
00:08:16,320 --> 00:08:16,839
Hyah!

105
00:08:22,679 --> 00:08:23,440
Whoa

106
00:08:23,839 --> 00:08:24,679
Whoa

107
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:27,040
I'll make two sachets for you.

108
00:08:27,640 --> 00:08:28,519
They're for repelling insects.

109
00:08:28,679 --> 00:08:29,399
Here.

110
00:08:33,640 --> 00:08:35,000
I'm willing to never marry for the rest of my life.

111
00:08:35,799 --> 00:08:37,200
To help her fulfill her wish.

112
00:08:39,760 --> 00:08:40,919
Fei Ying, what's wrong?

113
00:08:41,479 --> 00:08:42,320
It's nothing.

114
00:08:42,880 --> 00:08:44,479
My body just hasn't fully adjusted yet.

115
00:08:44,520 --> 00:08:45,640
I just regained my memory.

116
00:08:46,039 --> 00:08:47,359
Godfather has waited for us for seven years.

117
00:08:47,479 --> 00:08:48,520
Let's hurry back.

118
00:08:51,239 --> 00:08:51,880
Giddy up

119
00:08:52,719 --> 00:08:53,320
Giddy up

120
00:08:54,880 --> 00:08:55,520
Giddy up

121
00:08:56,479 --> 00:08:57,119
Giddy up

122
00:08:57,359 --> 00:08:59,559
Why is that person running so fast?

123
00:09:00,280 --> 00:09:01,719
Maybe he got stung by a wasp.

124
00:09:03,840 --> 00:09:05,039
Fei Ying, you...

125
00:09:05,840 --> 00:09:08,200
You seem different from before.

126
00:09:08,640 --> 00:09:09,559
Even more...

127
00:09:10,440 --> 00:09:11,799
You like to joke around even more now.

128
00:09:12,400 --> 00:09:13,200
It's been seven years.

129
00:09:13,239 --> 00:09:14,280
People change.

130
00:09:14,359 --> 00:09:15,239
You have too.

131
00:09:15,559 --> 00:09:16,440
You've become more attractive.

132
00:09:18,679 --> 00:09:19,520
Giddy up

133
00:09:20,080 --> 00:09:20,919
Giddy up

134
00:09:27,799 --> 00:09:29,080
You've just started to recover.

135
00:09:29,159 --> 00:09:30,039
Don't catch a chill.

136
00:09:30,159 --> 00:09:31,159
Go back inside quickly.

137
00:09:32,479 --> 00:09:33,320
You can't go in.

138
00:09:33,640 --> 00:09:34,440
You can't go in. Move aside.

139
00:09:34,520 --> 00:09:36,359
You can't barge in here. I'm here to find someone.

140
00:09:36,719 --> 00:09:37,599
What's going on?

141
00:09:37,679 --> 00:09:39,000
This is the person I'm looking for.

142
00:09:39,239 --> 00:09:40,239
Who are you?

143
00:09:40,919 --> 00:09:42,280
I'm her uncle.

144
00:09:45,440 --> 00:09:46,440
Uncle.

145
00:09:59,280 --> 00:10:01,119
Is he really my uncle?

146
00:10:02,719 --> 00:10:03,840
Judging by how much he eats,

147
00:10:04,119 --> 00:10:05,239
he really does seem like it.

148
00:10:08,080 --> 00:10:09,000
May I ask,

149
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:10,840
how did you find me?

150
00:10:15,599 --> 00:10:17,760
Thanks to these little ones.

151
00:10:19,119 --> 00:10:21,320
How did the bees know where I was?

152
00:10:24,679 --> 00:10:26,159
That's a long story.

153
00:10:26,679 --> 00:10:28,760
It's normal for you to doubt my identity right now.

154
00:10:29,559 --> 00:10:31,440
After all, we've never met.

155
00:10:31,760 --> 00:10:34,200
And there's no keepsake to prove it.

156
00:10:34,799 --> 00:10:36,239
It's hard to believe.

157
00:10:36,679 --> 00:10:37,440
By the way,

158
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:39,039
your father,

159
00:10:39,640 --> 00:10:40,960
he grinds his teeth when he sleeps.

160
00:10:41,280 --> 00:10:42,679
I still remember

161
00:10:42,840 --> 00:10:45,359
the year I first started working as a coroner at the yamen.

162
00:10:45,919 --> 00:10:47,400
One night, in the middle of the night,

163
00:10:47,760 --> 00:10:50,159
someone from the yamen suddenly came to call me for an autopsy.

164
00:10:50,520 --> 00:10:52,440
I heard your father's teeth grinding.

165
00:10:52,799 --> 00:10:55,440
I thought it was a corpse coming back to life in the coffin.

166
00:10:55,679 --> 00:10:57,359
I was so scared I fainted on the spot.

167
00:10:57,919 --> 00:10:58,840
So, looking at it this way,

168
00:10:59,119 --> 00:11:00,440
he really is your uncle.

169
00:11:02,039 --> 00:11:03,640
Before my father died, he said

170
00:11:03,799 --> 00:11:04,840
as long as I arrived in Mist Town,

171
00:11:04,880 --> 00:11:06,359
my uncle would come to find me.

172
00:11:07,559 --> 00:11:09,159
Now that I've met you,

173
00:11:09,640 --> 00:11:11,599
I've fulfilled my father's last wish.

174
00:11:11,840 --> 00:11:12,359
No,

175
00:11:12,479 --> 00:11:13,119
your father,

176
00:11:13,159 --> 00:11:15,039
your father has died.

177
00:11:18,960 --> 00:11:20,719
It was all done by the Tianluo people.

178
00:11:20,840 --> 00:11:22,599
Darn it, Tianluo.

179
00:11:24,479 --> 00:11:25,599
It's been twenty years,

180
00:11:26,400 --> 00:11:28,320
and we still couldn't escape them.

181
00:11:30,640 --> 00:11:32,799
I heard Linlang's uncle has arrived.

182
00:11:38,599 --> 00:11:39,479
Hall of Wind and Thunder

183
00:11:39,640 --> 00:11:40,760
Jiangbei Branch

184
00:11:40,880 --> 00:11:41,799
Xu Wenyuan

185
00:11:41,919 --> 00:11:43,599
Greetings, Third Hall Master

186
00:11:44,479 --> 00:11:46,000
You are a former member of the Hall of Wind and Thunder

187
00:11:46,359 --> 00:11:47,679
What is going on here?

188
00:11:47,719 --> 00:11:49,320
Before your father passed away

189
00:11:49,400 --> 00:11:50,520
He should have told you

190
00:11:51,080 --> 00:11:52,159
Your biological parents

191
00:11:52,280 --> 00:11:53,679
Should be someone else

192
00:11:53,799 --> 00:11:54,559
That's right

193
00:11:54,960 --> 00:11:56,239
My father said so

194
00:11:56,479 --> 00:11:57,760
As long as I acknowledge you

195
00:11:57,840 --> 00:11:59,159
You will tell me everything

196
00:12:04,719 --> 00:12:05,520
Back then,

197
00:12:05,599 --> 00:12:06,640
Master Luofeng

198
00:12:06,880 --> 00:12:08,119
did not care about one's background

199
00:12:08,320 --> 00:12:10,119
and recruited talented people from all over the world.

200
00:12:10,799 --> 00:12:11,960
My brother and I

201
00:12:12,159 --> 00:12:15,239
were also fortunate to be recruited into the Jiangbei branch.

202
00:12:15,599 --> 00:12:18,000
Master Luofeng, in order to spread medical knowledge,

203
00:12:18,320 --> 00:12:19,919
invited heroes from all over the land.

204
00:12:19,960 --> 00:12:21,479
Even my brother and I,

205
00:12:21,640 --> 00:12:23,080
who were just nobodies,

206
00:12:23,200 --> 00:12:25,000
were invited to join.

207
00:12:25,200 --> 00:12:26,440
It was a great honor.

208
00:12:26,479 --> 00:12:27,239
Kill!

209
00:12:27,400 --> 00:12:29,039
Who would have thought that the second hall master, Li Chu,

210
00:12:29,559 --> 00:12:30,799
would collude with Tianluo

211
00:12:31,119 --> 00:12:32,440
and attack Fenglei Hall,

212
00:12:32,679 --> 00:12:34,200
leaving it in a bloody massacre.

213
00:12:36,119 --> 00:12:37,080
Luolang

214
00:12:37,479 --> 00:12:38,599
Luolang! Madam!

215
00:12:38,799 --> 00:12:39,559
Hurry, go!

216
00:12:39,719 --> 00:12:40,559
My brother and I

217
00:12:40,679 --> 00:12:42,559
had only just joined Fenglei Hall,

218
00:12:42,679 --> 00:12:43,919
and our faces were still unfamiliar.

219
00:12:44,159 --> 00:12:45,719
Li Chu did not recognize us.

220
00:12:46,640 --> 00:12:48,039
Thanks to Madam's trust,

221
00:12:48,119 --> 00:12:49,520
she entrusted the newborn baby girl

222
00:12:49,640 --> 00:12:51,320
to the care of my brother and me.

223
00:12:52,440 --> 00:12:53,520
This baby girl

224
00:12:54,280 --> 00:12:55,479
was Linlang.

225
00:12:56,400 --> 00:12:58,119
But just like Master Luo,

226
00:12:58,320 --> 00:13:00,200
she was born with a unique fragrance.

227
00:13:00,359 --> 00:13:01,799
It was very easy for others to notice.

228
00:13:02,520 --> 00:13:04,440
To cover our escape,

229
00:13:05,840 --> 00:13:06,840
Madam actually...

230
00:13:36,080 --> 00:13:37,719
Alright, come over and have a drink.

231
00:13:45,080 --> 00:13:47,679
In order not to let down the trust of the master and madam,

232
00:13:48,239 --> 00:13:49,159
each of us...

233
00:13:49,280 --> 00:13:51,000
Kept Linlang hidden in the coffin shop

234
00:13:51,080 --> 00:13:53,000
Used medicine to suppress her natural scent

235
00:13:53,159 --> 00:13:54,960
And masked it further with the smell of corpses

236
00:13:57,559 --> 00:13:58,919
Take a break before playing again

237
00:14:01,440 --> 00:14:02,400
The other one

238
00:14:03,400 --> 00:14:04,559
Traveled everywhere

239
00:14:04,640 --> 00:14:06,359
To gather information about Li Chu

240
00:14:06,479 --> 00:14:07,599
To guard against any mishaps

241
00:14:09,880 --> 00:14:11,200
And relied on Fenglei Hall

242
00:14:11,320 --> 00:14:13,000
And their specially raised bees

243
00:14:13,280 --> 00:14:15,239
To sense Linlang's unique scent

244
00:14:15,479 --> 00:14:16,880
And share information

245
00:14:27,919 --> 00:14:29,719
I am actually the daughter of Master Luo

246
00:14:32,479 --> 00:14:33,359
I got it

247
00:14:36,960 --> 00:14:38,000
Linlang's hairpin

248
00:14:38,039 --> 00:14:40,559
It really matches the earrings Madam gave me

249
00:14:43,159 --> 00:14:44,200
For many years

250
00:14:44,479 --> 00:14:46,239
To protect Linlang's safety

251
00:14:46,359 --> 00:14:48,039
We didn't dare to acknowledge each other

252
00:14:48,479 --> 00:14:49,719
Just a few months ago

253
00:14:49,960 --> 00:14:52,359
We noticed the bees were unusually agitated

254
00:14:52,840 --> 00:14:54,359
And knew something had happened

255
00:14:55,039 --> 00:14:57,320
Linlang's scent could no longer be suppressed

256
00:14:57,440 --> 00:14:59,359
Li Chu would soon discover her

257
00:15:00,320 --> 00:15:01,159
So

258
00:15:01,440 --> 00:15:02,760
I traveled day and night

259
00:15:03,000 --> 00:15:04,440
Guided by the bees

260
00:15:04,520 --> 00:15:05,760
I arrived here

261
00:15:09,479 --> 00:15:11,280
Xu Xiang, Third Master of Fenglei Hall

262
00:15:11,359 --> 00:15:12,679
Respectfully invites the Young Master

263
00:15:12,840 --> 00:15:14,200
To restore Fenglei Hall

264
00:15:14,320 --> 00:15:15,840
Respectfully invites the Young Master

265
00:15:15,919 --> 00:15:17,520
To restore Fenglei Hall

266
00:15:18,400 --> 00:15:20,200
But I don't know how to do anything

267
00:15:20,919 --> 00:15:22,239
You are just like Master Luo

268
00:15:22,599 --> 00:15:24,400
With a heart to help the world

269
00:15:24,599 --> 00:15:25,960
This is the foundation of Fenglei Hall

270
00:15:26,159 --> 00:15:28,000
Master Luo and his wife, in the afterlife

271
00:15:28,440 --> 00:15:29,479
Would surely want to see you

272
00:15:29,520 --> 00:15:31,000
Complete their unfinished work

273
00:15:39,200 --> 00:15:40,559
Revive Fengleitang

274
00:15:41,159 --> 00:15:42,960
Luofeng's child is not dead

275
00:15:43,640 --> 00:15:46,400
And it's the girl who stays by Feiying's side

276
00:15:47,760 --> 00:15:49,239
It's been twenty years

277
00:15:49,799 --> 00:15:51,440
I've been investigating all this time

278
00:15:51,640 --> 00:15:54,200
The secret of the treasure Luofeng hid before his death

279
00:15:55,080 --> 00:15:57,520
Unfortunately, my efforts were wasted in the wrong direction

