00:16:03,679 --> 00:16:05,039
You useless fool

282
00:16:07,080 --> 00:16:08,320
I'm a fool?

283
00:16:08,719 --> 00:16:10,080
Then what are you?

284
00:16:12,200 --> 00:16:14,919
You sent one son to Tianluo as a hostage

285
00:16:15,200 --> 00:16:15,880
And the other

286
00:16:16,440 --> 00:16:18,960
You used as a stepping stone for your ambitions in the martial world

287
00:16:24,599 --> 00:16:25,880
This morning's tea

288
00:16:26,159 --> 00:16:27,159
Wasn't bad, was it?

289
00:16:27,239 --> 00:16:28,320
Ungrateful child

290
00:16:28,479 --> 00:16:29,719
How dare you

291
00:16:30,760 --> 00:16:31,919
I intended to keep you

292
00:16:32,119 --> 00:16:33,520
To restrain Feiying

293
00:16:33,760 --> 00:16:35,239
But now the most crucial clue

294
00:16:35,320 --> 00:16:37,039
Is actually with Xu Linlang

295
00:16:37,760 --> 00:16:39,400
Then you are of no use anymore

296
00:16:43,719 --> 00:16:46,200
In the face of wealth that rivals a nation

297
00:16:46,479 --> 00:16:48,359
Family ties are not worth mentioning at all

298
00:16:49,239 --> 00:16:51,359
This is what you taught Feiying back then

299
00:16:51,799 --> 00:16:52,960
My father

300
00:17:05,239 --> 00:17:05,880
Father

301
00:17:06,079 --> 00:17:07,719
I have brought Feiying back, father

302
00:17:08,439 --> 00:17:09,280
Good

303
00:17:09,359 --> 00:17:10,839
I have told you before

304
00:17:10,880 --> 00:17:12,520
Success depends on human effort

305
00:17:12,920 --> 00:17:15,079
You will surely achieve what you wish for

306
00:17:15,839 --> 00:17:16,839
Feiying has returned late

307
00:17:16,920 --> 00:17:18,160
Please punish me, foster father

308
00:17:18,280 --> 00:17:19,239
It's fine

309
00:17:19,400 --> 00:17:20,959
Get up and speak

310
00:17:23,920 --> 00:17:25,160
Seven years ago

311
00:17:25,239 --> 00:17:28,119
You found the location of the Wuxiang treasure

312
00:17:28,239 --> 00:17:30,359
That was a great achievement

313
00:17:36,400 --> 00:17:37,280
Father

314
00:17:37,719 --> 00:17:40,119
Fei Ying was injured by a magical artifact in the Tianchi cemetery.

315
00:17:40,359 --> 00:17:42,680
Although most of his memories have already returned,

316
00:17:42,880 --> 00:17:45,040
he still hasn't recalled anything about the Wuxiang Treasure.

317
00:17:45,439 --> 00:17:46,920
He has yet to remember.

318
00:17:47,239 --> 00:17:48,079
Foster father

319
00:17:48,439 --> 00:17:51,280
You have three pieces of the Wuxiang Treasure map.

320
00:17:51,760 --> 00:17:52,680
The last piece

321
00:17:52,760 --> 00:17:54,439
should be in the hands of the remaining members of Fenglei Hall.

322
00:17:54,959 --> 00:17:55,640
Fei Ying

323
00:17:55,760 --> 00:17:57,319
is willing to retrieve it for you, foster father.

324
00:18:01,359 --> 00:18:03,880
Since you are so filial,

325
00:18:04,520 --> 00:18:06,359
do not disappoint me.

326
00:18:06,880 --> 00:18:07,760
Yes.

327
00:18:58,319 --> 00:18:59,160
Sima Kong

328
00:18:59,239 --> 00:19:00,920
You really are a master strategist.

329
00:19:00,959 --> 00:19:01,959
If it weren't for you,

330
00:19:02,119 --> 00:19:03,760
I would have been riddled with holes by now.

331
00:19:05,199 --> 00:19:06,439
Even though I've lost all my martial arts skills,

332
00:19:06,520 --> 00:19:07,359
being by your side

333
00:19:07,439 --> 00:19:08,479
still means I'm not completely useless, right?

334
00:19:08,520 --> 00:19:09,640
I'm impressed, truly.

335
00:19:09,800 --> 00:19:11,760
No wonder you're the top strategist of Fenglei Hall.

336
00:19:12,280 --> 00:19:13,239
But

337
00:19:13,680 --> 00:19:15,520
how did you know that person's tactics?

338
00:19:17,920 --> 00:19:18,959
He's from the Tang Clan.

339
00:19:19,119 --> 00:19:20,280
Someone from the Tang Clan?

340
00:19:33,079 --> 00:19:34,839
Thank you, Young Master, for sparing my life.

341
00:19:35,599 --> 00:19:36,439
With this injury,

342
00:19:37,000 --> 00:19:39,079
I can finally return and report back.

343
00:19:42,079 --> 00:19:44,199
You made sure his wound wasn't fatal,

344
00:19:44,280 --> 00:19:45,520
and he can still go back to complete his mission.

345
00:19:45,920 --> 00:19:47,520
Just like I said earlier,

346
00:19:47,880 --> 00:19:49,560
you're truly a master strategist.

347
00:19:49,959 --> 00:19:52,079
Even when you go easy on someone, you do it so skillfully.

348
00:19:53,599 --> 00:19:55,079
Old Yan is no different.

349
00:19:55,640 --> 00:19:56,920
What do you mean?

350
00:19:57,319 --> 00:19:58,880
He has worked with me for over ten years,

351
00:19:59,119 --> 00:20:00,520
and we both trained in the Tang Clan.

352
00:20:01,119 --> 00:20:02,640
How could he not anticipate my traps?

353
00:20:04,280 --> 00:20:06,680
You always seemed so cold and distant before,

354
00:20:06,920 --> 00:20:08,880
but no one values loyalty more than you.

355
00:20:10,599 --> 00:20:11,319
Look,

356
00:20:11,599 --> 00:20:12,920
you look so nice when you smile.

357
00:20:20,680 --> 00:20:22,520
Are they also from the Tang Clan?

358
00:20:28,079 --> 00:20:28,839
No.

359
00:20:29,839 --> 00:20:30,880
But his moves

360
00:20:30,959 --> 00:20:32,239
seem strangely familiar.

361
00:20:36,239 --> 00:20:38,040
As the mantis stalks the cicada, the oriole waits behind.

362
00:20:38,560 --> 00:20:39,520
With just you all,

363
00:20:39,599 --> 00:20:40,479
Lu Jiu

364
00:20:42,760 --> 00:20:43,920
I'm not Lu Jiu.

365
00:20:47,920 --> 00:20:48,560
Lu Jiu

366
00:20:48,719 --> 00:20:50,280
I trust you won't hurt me.

367
00:20:50,439 --> 00:20:52,439
Stop pretending you understand me.

368
00:20:52,959 --> 00:20:54,079
Why don't we give it a try?

369
00:20:54,239 --> 00:20:54,920
Lu Jiu

370
00:20:55,439 --> 00:20:55,839
No.

371
00:20:55,959 --> 00:20:56,719
Fei Ying

372
00:20:57,239 --> 00:20:57,959
Let her go.

373
00:20:58,599 --> 00:20:59,839
I'll do anything you want.

374
00:21:00,400 --> 00:21:01,319
What a pity.

375
00:21:01,760 --> 00:21:03,359
You're someone whose martial arts were crippled by Tangmen.

376
00:21:03,400 --> 00:21:04,560
Trying to negotiate with me.

377
00:21:05,079 --> 00:21:06,079
Are you even qualified?

378
00:21:17,439 --> 00:21:18,239
Lu Jiu

379
00:21:18,800 --> 00:21:20,560
It's not too late for you to come over to the right side now.

380
00:21:20,959 --> 00:21:22,680
Even if you've forgotten everything from the past,

381
00:21:22,760 --> 00:21:24,319
you still can't help the wicked do evil.

382
00:21:25,319 --> 00:21:26,719
I advise you to be honest.

383
00:21:27,719 --> 00:21:28,640
Xiao Jiu

384
00:21:30,400 --> 00:21:31,359
It's you.

385
00:21:32,359 --> 00:21:33,239
Xiao Jiu

386
00:21:34,239 --> 00:21:35,359
It's me.

387
00:21:36,400 --> 00:21:37,920
Your eldest brother who cares for you the most.

388
00:21:38,119 --> 00:21:39,280
As far as I know,

389
00:21:40,719 --> 00:21:42,079
back in Luoyang County,

390
00:21:42,280 --> 00:21:43,719
you planned an elaborate escape.

391
00:21:43,920 --> 00:21:45,719
You wanted to put me in mortal danger.

392
00:21:46,920 --> 00:21:47,839
Xiao Jiu

393
00:21:49,839 --> 00:21:51,680
Your big brother had his own difficulties.

394
00:21:51,880 --> 00:21:53,119
I don't know martial arts.

395
00:21:53,599 --> 00:21:54,880
My schemes can't compare to yours.

396
00:21:54,959 --> 00:21:56,079
Long ago, I already

397
00:21:56,239 --> 00:21:57,880
became the one Father abandoned.

398
00:21:58,319 --> 00:21:59,479
When I ran away back then,

399
00:22:00,280 --> 00:22:01,280
it was only

400
00:22:01,560 --> 00:22:03,400
to escape death.

401
00:22:04,760 --> 00:22:06,040
Today, I came here

402
00:22:06,479 --> 00:22:07,760
just to remind you

403
00:22:07,920 --> 00:22:09,119
to be careful of Father.

404
00:22:09,319 --> 00:22:09,920
Lu Jiu

405
00:22:10,000 --> 00:22:11,199
Don't let him deceive you.

406
00:22:11,400 --> 00:22:12,400
With Li Chu's cunning,

407
00:22:12,479 --> 00:22:14,359
how could he possibly have time to warn anyone?

408
00:22:20,079 --> 00:22:21,000
Xiao Jiu

409
00:22:21,439 --> 00:22:22,920
I don't have much time left.

410
00:22:23,880 --> 00:22:26,040
I've heard that the Wuxiang Treasure

411
00:22:26,439 --> 00:22:28,800
contains medical texts that can cure all diseases.

412
00:22:29,520 --> 00:22:30,719
I came here today

413
00:22:30,920 --> 00:22:31,959
hoping that

414
00:22:32,199 --> 00:22:34,199
for the sake of our brotherhood,

415
00:22:34,839 --> 00:22:36,359
if you find the treasure one day,

416
00:22:37,560 --> 00:22:38,760
you could

417
00:22:39,239 --> 00:22:40,640
find a cure for me.

418
00:22:42,719 --> 00:22:43,719
Big Brother

419
00:22:44,319 --> 00:22:45,319
Xiao Jiu

420
00:22:52,079 --> 00:22:53,119
In the past,

421
00:22:53,880 --> 00:22:55,680
you deceived Lu Jiu like this, didn't you?

422
00:23:00,800 --> 00:23:02,280
Weren't you supposed to not know martial arts?

423
00:23:02,760 --> 00:23:03,560
So why

424
00:23:04,079 --> 00:23:05,920
did you get exposed so quickly?

425
00:23:08,079 --> 00:23:08,959
Fei Ying

426
00:23:09,239 --> 00:23:10,520
Do you think that regaining your memory

427
00:23:10,640 --> 00:23:11,959
and returning to Tianluo

428
00:23:12,280 --> 00:23:14,119
will make Dugu trust you?

429
00:23:16,160 --> 00:23:17,719
You're too naive.

430
00:23:19,239 --> 00:23:20,400
He just

431
00:23:20,640 --> 00:23:21,760
wants to get from you

432
00:23:21,800 --> 00:23:24,439
the key clues about the Wuxiang Treasure.

433
00:23:25,239 --> 00:23:26,439
Other than that,

434
00:23:26,599 --> 00:23:28,040
you're worthless.

435
00:23:30,560 --> 00:23:31,439
Is that so?

436
00:23:34,479 --> 00:23:35,680
One day,

437
00:23:36,199 --> 00:23:37,719
I'll make you pay.

438
00:23:42,520 --> 00:23:43,280
Let's go.

439
00:23:56,760 --> 00:23:58,119
Fei Ying reporting back.

440
00:23:58,439 --> 00:23:59,359
Good.

441
00:23:59,959 --> 00:24:02,199
You truly are my good disciple.

442
00:24:10,959 --> 00:24:11,800
You scoundrel.

443
00:24:12,000 --> 00:24:14,079
His Majesty established Tianluo to secure the nation.

444
00:24:14,160 --> 00:24:15,920
But you raise assassins for your own gain.

445
00:24:16,319 --> 00:24:18,119
You even slaughtered Fenglei Hall to seize the treasure.

446
00:24:18,160 --> 00:24:19,479
You will face divine retribution sooner or later.

447
00:24:19,520 --> 00:24:21,040
Divine retribution?

448
00:24:21,479 --> 00:24:22,319
I

449
00:24:22,680 --> 00:24:24,359
am the heavens.

450
00:24:27,880 --> 00:24:28,959
Luo Feng.

451
00:24:29,520 --> 00:24:31,400
Do you think that by refusing to confess,

452
00:24:31,439 --> 00:24:34,000
I won't be able to find the treasure's location?

453
00:24:34,199 --> 00:24:35,000
Look,

454
00:24:35,040 --> 00:24:37,359
your daughter is in my hands right now.

455
00:24:37,479 --> 00:24:39,959
Do you think I’ll have trouble finding the treasure?

456
00:24:42,800 --> 00:24:44,119
Do you think that regaining your memory

457
00:24:44,319 --> 00:24:45,560
and returning to Tianluo

458
00:24:46,000 --> 00:24:47,520
will make Dugu trust you?

459
00:24:48,119 --> 00:24:49,479
You’re too naive.

460
00:24:49,520 --> 00:24:50,599
He only

461
00:24:50,719 --> 00:24:51,880
wants to get from you

462
00:24:51,880 --> 00:24:54,560
the key clues about the Wuxiang treasure.

463
00:24:54,920 --> 00:24:56,199
Other than that,

464
00:24:56,319 --> 00:24:57,760
you’re worthless.

465
00:24:59,760 --> 00:25:01,439
I’m afraid you’ll be disappointed.

466
00:25:01,599 --> 00:25:03,680
I’ve never met my birth parents.

467
00:25:04,079 --> 00:25:05,680
Nor have I ever heard of any treasure.

468
00:25:06,479 --> 00:25:07,319
In fact,

469
00:25:07,479 --> 00:25:09,000
I should thank you all.

470
00:25:09,079 --> 00:25:10,479
If you hadn’t been hunting me all this time,

471
00:25:10,680 --> 00:25:12,680
I would never have learned about my own origins.

472
00:25:14,640 --> 00:25:16,520
Refusing a toast only to be forced to drink.

473
00:25:17,119 --> 00:25:18,239
Guards!

474
00:25:22,199 --> 00:25:24,119
Interrogate her thoroughly for me.

475
00:25:24,880 --> 00:25:25,359
Yes.

476
00:25:25,400 --> 00:25:26,280
Foster father.

477
00:25:28,280 --> 00:25:29,599
I was the one who captured her.

478
00:25:30,040 --> 00:25:31,160
Let me handle the interrogation.

479
00:25:31,199 --> 00:25:32,400
I will definitely make her reveal

480
00:25:32,640 --> 00:25:33,760
the clues to the treasure.

481
00:25:33,839 --> 00:25:34,880
No need.

482
00:25:37,400 --> 00:25:39,000
You just regained your memory.

483
00:25:39,359 --> 00:25:41,280
You still suffer from frequent headaches.

484
00:25:41,680 --> 00:25:43,680
I specially invited several renowned doctors

485
00:25:43,760 --> 00:25:45,319
to treat your illness.

486
00:25:46,119 --> 00:25:47,079
But

487
00:25:47,239 --> 00:25:48,719
your marriage with Yemei

488
00:25:48,839 --> 00:25:50,560
has been delayed for so many years.

489
00:25:50,760 --> 00:25:52,560
It's time to start preparing for it.

490
00:25:52,800 --> 00:25:54,119
These trivial matters

491
00:25:54,400 --> 00:25:56,800
can be left to the subordinates.

492
00:25:58,079 --> 00:25:59,000
Then, Feiying,

493
00:25:59,599 --> 00:26:00,560
I will take my leave first.

494
00:26:00,839 --> 00:26:01,599
Alright.

495
00:26:22,760 --> 00:26:23,479
Feiying.

496
00:26:23,599 --> 00:26:24,520
You're back.

497
00:26:24,959 --> 00:26:26,319
Didn't Senior Sister

498
00:26:26,800 --> 00:26:28,520
come back with me from the forest?

499
00:26:28,800 --> 00:26:30,560
How could you not know when I returned?

500
00:26:32,640 --> 00:26:33,400
Feiying.

501
00:26:33,839 --> 00:26:34,839
I didn't mean to...

502
00:26:34,880 --> 00:26:35,680
I understand.

503
00:26:36,920 --> 00:26:38,079
You are the foster father's daughter.

504
00:26:38,319 --> 00:26:39,560
You have to follow his orders.

505
00:27:05,000 --> 00:27:06,479
Lord Geng

506
00:27:09,280 --> 00:27:11,959
You currently hold no official position.

507
00:27:12,319 --> 00:27:13,599
So I should call you

508
00:27:13,719 --> 00:27:15,119
Brother Geng, right?

509
00:27:15,160 --> 00:27:16,800
His Majesty has long had doubts about the Fenglei Hall case.

510
00:27:16,839 --> 00:27:17,920
He has been suspicious.

511
00:27:18,119 --> 00:27:19,800
That's why he sent me to investigate.

512
00:27:20,760 --> 00:27:22,839
But now he doesn't trust me at all.

513
00:27:23,079 --> 00:27:23,920
I suppose

514
00:27:24,319 --> 00:27:25,599
Tianluo and Tang Clan

515
00:27:25,680 --> 00:27:27,280
have put a lot of effort into this.

516
00:27:29,000 --> 00:27:32,359
I really can't tell if you're clever or foolish.

517
00:27:32,560 --> 00:27:35,280
Whoever obtains the Wuxiang treasure will rule the world.

518
00:27:35,800 --> 00:27:39,199
That's why His Majesty fears Fenglei Hall so much.

519
00:27:40,119 --> 00:27:41,239
And you

520
00:27:41,520 --> 00:27:44,079
are siding with the remnants of Fenglei Hall.

521
00:27:44,280 --> 00:27:46,479
You're clearly seeking your own doom.

522
00:27:48,199 --> 00:27:49,400
Aren't you doing the same?

523
00:27:51,000 --> 00:27:52,280
The Tang Clan values their craftsmanship.

524
00:27:52,479 --> 00:27:53,760
They covet the Wuxiang treasure.

525
00:27:54,000 --> 00:27:55,400
I'm afraid it's not for gold or silver.

526
00:27:55,599 --> 00:27:56,680
But for what's inside—

527
00:27:56,760 --> 00:27:58,560
the weapon blueprints from the previous dynasty.

528
00:27:59,119 --> 00:28:00,079
But have you ever considered

529
00:28:00,160 --> 00:28:02,400
Dugu Wumo holds immense power over the court

530
00:28:02,800 --> 00:28:04,359
and still seeks the Wuxiang treasure

531
00:28:04,560 --> 00:28:06,479
Could it be that he harbors ambitions to usurp the throne?

532
00:28:06,560 --> 00:28:07,680
Our Tang Sect

533
00:28:07,800 --> 00:28:09,319
only does business

534
00:28:09,640 --> 00:28:11,239
As for court affairs

535
00:28:11,599 --> 00:28:12,880
we are not concerned

536
00:28:13,920 --> 00:28:15,400
The legendary

537
00:28:15,479 --> 00:28:16,959
blueprints of the previous dynasty's weapons

538
00:28:17,280 --> 00:28:19,160
were enough to cause the destruction of Fenglei Hall

539
00:28:19,239 --> 00:28:19,959
If

540
00:28:20,160 --> 00:28:22,079
Dugu Wumo's plot succeeds

541
00:28:22,160 --> 00:28:23,359
and he ascends the throne

542
00:28:23,520 --> 00:28:25,359
would he allow it to remain in this world?

543
00:28:25,640 --> 00:28:26,520
Geng Zhao

544
00:28:27,280 --> 00:28:30,000
do not try to sow discord between Tang Sect and Tianluo

545
00:28:30,280 --> 00:28:31,880
It is because I value your talent

546
00:28:31,959 --> 00:28:33,199
that I came to visit

547
00:28:33,800 --> 00:28:35,199
Do not be stubborn and refuse to listen

548
00:28:35,800 --> 00:28:37,079
or you will harm yourself

549
00:28:37,160 --> 00:28:38,760
and drag others down with you

550
00:28:39,800 --> 00:28:41,000
You will harm others

551
00:28:46,319 --> 00:28:47,560
Why are you here?

552
00:28:52,640 --> 00:28:55,319
What virtue or ability do you possess, Geng Zhao

553
00:28:56,119 --> 00:28:57,880
to make the princess

554
00:28:58,000 --> 00:28:59,479
in the Golden Throne Hall

555
00:28:59,520 --> 00:29:00,800
take all the blame

556
00:29:00,880 --> 00:29:03,280
for the rebellion at Gushan by herself?

557
00:29:04,119 --> 00:29:05,319
Though she is a princess

558
00:29:05,599 --> 00:29:06,599
in the Department of Investigation

559
00:29:06,640 --> 00:29:08,040
she is merely my subordinate

560
00:29:08,359 --> 00:29:10,319
How could she have accomplished all this alone?

561
00:29:10,359 --> 00:29:12,680
His Majesty does not care about this matter

562
00:29:14,439 --> 00:29:15,880
If you fall

563
00:29:16,160 --> 00:29:18,000
Who will restrain Tianluo?

564
00:29:20,319 --> 00:29:21,520
It's just a pity.

565
00:29:21,599 --> 00:29:23,560
Her Highness the Princess has been wronged.

566
00:29:23,959 --> 00:29:24,640
Lord Geng.

567
00:29:24,760 --> 00:29:25,520
Please leave.

568
00:29:25,599 --> 00:29:27,560
This cell is to be vacated for Her Highness the Princess.

569
00:29:29,920 --> 00:29:31,680
This concerns the grave crime of treason.

570
00:29:32,479 --> 00:29:34,439
Even Her Highness the Princess

571
00:29:34,839 --> 00:29:36,359
cannot escape the death penalty.

572
00:29:36,959 --> 00:29:38,719
Let them talk a little longer.

573
00:29:39,880 --> 00:29:41,319
On the road to the afterlife,

574
00:29:42,239 --> 00:29:44,000
they can rest in peace.

575
00:29:55,599 --> 00:29:56,959
Don't overthink it.

576
00:29:58,520 --> 00:30:01,000
I just pity the wronged souls of Fenglei Hall.

577
00:30:02,000 --> 00:30:03,119
It's not for you.

578
00:30:03,400 --> 00:30:04,560
Back at Gushan,

579
00:30:04,880 --> 00:30:06,040
I already anticipated

580
00:30:06,520 --> 00:30:07,520
that defying the imperial decree

581
00:30:07,839 --> 00:30:09,199
would lead to a dangerous path ahead.

582
00:30:09,800 --> 00:30:11,199
I didn't want to implicate you.

583
00:30:11,959 --> 00:30:12,839
I never expected

584
00:30:13,000 --> 00:30:14,520
that in the end, I still harmed you.

585
00:30:16,239 --> 00:30:17,239
Are you saying

586
00:30:18,640 --> 00:30:20,439
that you were so cold to me before

587
00:30:22,239 --> 00:30:24,119
because you didn't want to drag me down?

588
00:30:26,839 --> 00:30:28,319
I, Geng Zhao, have investigated cases for half my life.

589
00:30:28,680 --> 00:30:31,000
I've lived every day on the edge, risking my life.

590
00:30:31,280 --> 00:30:32,959
I never dared to think of burdening someone dear.

591
00:30:34,479 --> 00:30:35,479
Until

592
00:30:36,959 --> 00:30:37,920
I met you.

593
00:30:44,280 --> 00:30:45,400
I knew then

594
00:30:47,000 --> 00:30:49,439
I knew you cared about me.

595
00:30:52,479 --> 00:30:53,920
I should have told you long ago.

596
00:30:58,800 --> 00:31:00,119
Hearing you say that,

597
00:31:02,640 --> 00:31:03,880
I could die without regrets.

598
00:31:06,359 --> 00:31:07,239
Don't worry.

599
00:31:07,800 --> 00:31:09,319
I will definitely get you out of here.

600
00:31:11,160 --> 00:31:12,199
This secret room

601
00:31:12,239 --> 00:31:13,800
was carefully designed just for you.

602
00:31:14,959 --> 00:31:17,000
Even if you can hear sounds from outside,

603
00:31:17,359 --> 00:31:19,520
they won't be able to find any trace of you.

604
00:31:19,959 --> 00:31:21,479
What exactly do you want?

605
00:31:21,800 --> 00:31:23,680
I've already told you, I don't know where the treasure is.

606
00:31:25,520 --> 00:31:27,280
Do you think that if you refuse to talk,

607
00:31:27,479 --> 00:31:28,920
they'll let you go?

608
00:31:29,479 --> 00:31:30,079
No.

609
00:31:30,479 --> 00:31:32,520
If you have no value to them anymore,

610
00:31:32,640 --> 00:31:34,079
you'll only die faster.

611
00:31:35,479 --> 00:31:36,400
Maybe

612
00:31:36,560 --> 00:31:38,239
they'll even have Fei Ying finish you off himself.

613
00:31:38,319 --> 00:31:39,760
You're just like Dugu.

614
00:31:40,160 --> 00:31:42,319
You only treat him as a killing tool.

615
00:31:42,359 --> 00:31:43,719
You've never really thought about him.

616
00:31:43,800 --> 00:31:44,719
Shut up.

617
00:31:46,000 --> 00:31:48,079
Fei Ying is the most important person to me.

618
00:31:48,599 --> 00:31:50,319
No one understands him better than I do.

619
00:31:50,520 --> 00:31:52,280
No one cares about him more than I do.

620
00:31:52,800 --> 00:31:54,640
You were only with him when he lost his memory

621
00:31:54,680 --> 00:31:56,079
and spent a few days with him.

622
00:31:56,199 --> 00:31:58,400
You could never shake my place in his heart.

623
00:31:58,439 --> 00:31:59,880
Why are you getting so worked up?

624
00:32:00,479 --> 00:32:01,520
I guess

625
00:32:01,760 --> 00:32:03,040
Dugu and Feiying

626
00:32:03,119 --> 00:32:05,160
have no idea you came to see me.

627
00:32:07,359 --> 00:32:08,560
That's none of your business.

628
00:32:09,280 --> 00:32:10,920
I'm the one who's winning now.

629
00:32:11,199 --> 00:32:12,920
Feiying was always mine to begin with.

630
00:32:14,079 --> 00:32:15,280
To be honest,

631
00:32:15,640 --> 00:32:17,959
when I first learned you were engaged to Lu Jiu,

632
00:32:18,359 --> 00:32:20,319
I was really heartbroken for a while.

633
00:32:21,520 --> 00:32:23,479
But later, I came to understand something.

634
00:32:26,000 --> 00:32:27,479
The things we've been through,

635
00:32:27,640 --> 00:32:28,920
the people in our hearts,

636
00:32:29,280 --> 00:32:31,000
will only hide in a corner of our hearts,

637
00:32:31,079 --> 00:32:32,719
but they'll never just disappear.

638
00:32:33,760 --> 00:32:35,280
If you can wait for Feiying to come back,

639
00:32:35,719 --> 00:32:37,119
then I can wait for Lu Jiu to return.
